title: 45 killed in Russian air strikes in Syria's Latakia: Monitor - Region - World
text: At least 45 people have been killed in a wave of Russian air strikes in the north of the regime stronghold of Latakia province, a monitor said on Tuesday. The Syrian Observatory for Human Right said civilians were among the dead in the strikes on Monday in Jabal al-Akrad, and that dozens more were wounded.
